    "brand": "NYX Professional Makeup",
    "title": "NYX Professional Makeup Buttermelt Blush - Than Before - 0.17oz",
    "description": "Butta blush. Butta boom! NYX Professional Makeup Buttermelt Blush comes in 12 highly pigmented, buttalicious shades that blends like powder & glides like butta, in soft matte and glowy finishes. Infused with mango butter, almond butter, & shea butter, it doesn't get any butta than this. Fade & transfer resistant. Up to 12 hours wear. Vegan and cruelty free. How To Use: Need a blush hack? Here's how to apply blush for a butta blend. Lightly tap your brush into the pan to pick up pigment, then swirl the brush on the high points of your cheek, around the temples, and even across the nose for a warm flush of blush. Layer over NYX Professional Makeup Buttermelt Bronzer for a warm natural sun-soaked bronzed look and make it butta together!"
  },
