    "at": 1782751780227,
    "brand": "L'Oreal Paris",
    "title": "L'Oreal Paris Telescopic Original Lengthening Mascara - 935 Carbon Black - 0.27 fl oz",
    "description": "L?Oreal Paris' Iconic Telescopic Original Washable Mascara delivers extreme length and ultimate definition for up to 70% longer lashes and up to 24 HR wear. The specially designed Precision Brush catches every lash for instant separation. This lightweight formula coats lashes in one stroke for clump-free, smudge-resistant, and flake-resistant results. Fragrance-free. Ophthalmologist-tested. Suitable for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers. Place the brush at the base of lashes and gently sweep up to tip. Pair with L?Oreal Paris Telescopic Precision Long Lasting Liquid Eyeliner for dramatic definition. Removes easily with makeup remover. Never pump your mascara wand, as this adds air to the mascara container, which will make your mascara dry out faster."
  },
